>每月任務</em></strong>：1. 換美金，走資2. 陪審員/派傳單/放映會/各有各做<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持；Best effort，你呢？民主尚未成功，同志仍需努力<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRgNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=67112f65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n理非可以做的事<a href=\"https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTakeActionWithYou&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRgNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=317cf77f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou</a><br />\n良心與無良商戶<a href=\"https://www.wordsofmouth.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wordsofmouth.net%2F&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRgNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=1f4e86da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wordsofmouth.net/</a><br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\nVersion 2019.09.26<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">極權如何打壓香港示威？<br />\n1.抹黑：利用少部分的暴力衝突而將全部示威者形容為「邪惡」、示威=港獨<br />\n2.誤導：送中條例、說謊、黃色object等等<br />\n3.滲透：5毛、陳雲、黃x民、譚香文<br />\n4.假民意/曲解民意：主流民意是......<br />\n5.5毛輿論-分化、負面、fake news、煽動手足做負效益/低效益工作<br />\n6.強迫企業自我審查<br />\n7.出動黑社會、愛國暴徒<br />\n8.扮示威者：(負面的)破壞eg.遊行<br />\n9.嫁禍示威者：打議員打記者打女仔<br />\n諗到再加</span>"},{"pid":"d6c7f8efbb401c28d9ceea3f54225581b2718b36","tid":1595251,"uid":275524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ef43eb864fc106c8d6fe5ec4346cbf46ce771ab","tid":1595251,"uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T03:11:46.000Z","msg":"請海外專家監督既意義 可能仲重要過個選舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T03:26:18.000Z","msg":"公平。公正。 公開"},{"pid":"de675f7a1013adc71c364bc94ceb9127a0ec0891","tid":1595251,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T03:36:43.000Z","msg":"香港正苦同獨裁政權無異，連選舉都要靠外國監察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.g